item.title: Welcome to OHEAL
item.description: Welcome Welcoem to the Oral Health Epidemiology & Analysis Lab. OHEAL focuses on oral health equity through the application of statistical epidemiology and policy development. Interested students or researchers should email Prof Ryan Ruff at ryan.ruff@nyu.edu. You can embed an R code chunk like this: summary(cars) ## speed dist ## Min. : 4.0 Min. : 2.00 ## 1st Qu.:12.0 1st Qu.: 26.00 ## Median :15.0 Median : 36.00 ## Mean :15.
